Installing Pydra:

1) update paths in pydra/config.py if needed
2) run setup.py in this folder.  requires root
3) set ownership/groups appropriately for these:
    config.RUNTIME
    config.RUNTIME_FILES_DIR
    config.LOGGING_DIR
4) update CONFIG_DIR/pydra_settings.py to contain your database information
5) create database with: pydra_manage syncdb
6) start pydra with pydra_master and pydra_node

Notes:
    * This installer does not yet allow variable configuration of config paths
